title._content: First Congregational Church, Central Square, Keene NH

description._content: TITLE First Congregational Church, Central Square, Keene NH CREATOR SUBJECT Churches - NH - Keene Congregational churches - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Photograph of the First Congregational Church (now the United Church of Christ) on Central Square in Keene New Hampshire. "Head of the Square, Keene, in 1901. The original church edifice was built in the park, and dedicated in 1788. In December, 1828, it was removed to the present location and a new front and steeple added. It was again remodeled as at present in 1859-60. All the other buildings shown have either undergone removal or substantial changes in appearance." PUBLISHER Keene Public Library DATE DIGITAL 20071130 DATE ORIGINAL 1901?
